headline: Essex Property Trust (NYSE:ESS) Tripled Earnings With US$2.57 Dividend Despite 5% Dip Last Quarter
summary: Essex Property Trust (NYSE:ESS) witnessed a price decline of 5% over the last quarter. During this period, the company announced a dividend of $2.57 per share and reported strong earnings growth, with Q4 net income more than tripling year-over-year. Despite its solid financial performance, the broader economic environment may have influenced its stock price, as the market experienced significant volatility due to global trade tensions.
